text: Tutu Sohlberg (born 8 August 1941) is a Finnish equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Finland Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Helsinki
